re trying to do is to record the story of your life as a statistician, or in statistics, and I think the first question I was interested in was whether there was any family influence in that \endash  were there people in your family at all \'85? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
