\par Claus:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 To keep account of the numbers and categories and so on. Would I like to help him? \'93Yes\'94. And that\rquote 
s how I became a statistician. Absolutely hundred per cent cause, because when I then went to LSE in the autumn that year \endash  because I was released quite quickly \endash 
 I did enrol in the B.Com., but I hated it. I hated commerce really, and I switched to statistics, because I was good at maths. And so it was a very simple causation \endash  imprisonment. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
