\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 So what did he teach you \endash  Landau? What did he teach you? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
