\par Claus:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 No, I was purely his helpmate, you know, keeping records of the numbers who came, who were ad
mitted, who were released, what we knew about them. Keeping records. I was like a minor statistical assistant, and I loved it, actually. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
