\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 Was that a new survey, or was that, again, using older material? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
