What sort of a country is this?\'94 I mean, that\rquote s really what I like doing, what I\rquote ve always liked doing. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
