\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 Can I ask you, you\rquote ve mentioned about sampling that you had some innovations, you made some innovations there. What were they? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
