\par Claus:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 Well, innovations would be - yeah, I suppose it\rquote s true, in the sense that for surveys, for surveys, whether it\rquote 
s opinion polls or commercial surveys, or serious government surveys, in the bad old days quota sampling was the most popular, where you decided on the numbers you want, and the categories you wanted to cover. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
