\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 There was one thing 
which we did speak about briefly, but there was a defect in the recording at that moment, and I wondered whether I can ask you again. It\rquote s about schools, and whether you had any maths teachers who were influential? What about Germany? I mean, it
\rquote s got such a high reputation \endash  German education. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5510798\charrsid5510798 
